.DT
special_add_property
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
special_add_property

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
special_add_property -  This method allows you to add properties onto players who are not currently logged on.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int special_add_property(string pname,
string prop,
mixed val)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^pname%^RESET%^ - name of player to change
%^BOLD%^prop%^RESET%^ - the property to change
%^BOLD%^val%^RESET%^ - the new value for it
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 upon success, 0 upon failure

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/secure/login.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method allows you to add properties onto players who are not
currently logged on.
.EP

